data.description: Great 4 bedroom 2 bath home close to town, but just far enough away to feel like country living. There is a large yard with no HOA and its just outside of the city limits.  This home boasts new carpet and LVP flooring throughout.  There are new blinds, fresh paint, new back deck, and screen porch.  Its move in ready for you and your family.
